import React from 'react';
import Navbar from "react-bootstrap/Navbar"
import Nav from "react-bootstrap/Nav"

function Header() {
  return (
    <Navbar expand="lg">
      <Navbar.Brand href="#home">TEMPO</Navbar.Brand>
      <Nav variant="tabs">
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/browse">Browse Courses</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link href="/current">Current Courses</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Link onSelect={() => console.log('this is working')} href="/classroom">Classroom</Nav.Link>
        </Nav.Item>
      </Nav>
    </Navbar>
  )
}

export default Header;
